cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with 3D object reconstruction using deep learning and robotics. The most relevant sub-category is likely to be computer vision (cs.CV) as the paper deals with 3D sensing technology and object reconstruction. Robotics (cs.RO) is also a likely sub-category as the paper discusses the use of low-cost robotic platforms for object reconstruction. Machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) are also relevant sub-categories as the paper proposes a novel next-best-view planning scheme based on supervised deep learning. Finally, computer graphics (cs.GR) is a possible sub-category as the paper deals with the reconstruction of unknown objects in 3D space.
